title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1994-02-27
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Row Jimmy, Minglewood Blues, Lazy River Road, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Tennessee Jed, Easy Answers

Set 2

Touch Of Gray, Samson & Delilah, Uncle John's Band-> Corinna-> Dragon parade-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Cosmic Charlie tease-> Wharf Rat-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Rain

first "Mama Tried" since 01-25-93. "Supplication" jam during "Uncle John's". "Cosmic Charlie" tease before "Wharf Rat". Dragon parade during Drums.
